1.0.name: wordpress/ap-schema
1.0.description:
AP Schema provides an easy way to create a revie summary box in your posts and pages. This information is combined with your google plus account in order to show your rating as stars in the search results.

A Google plus account is required if you want the stars in the search results, but not required for the plugin to create a review box on your site.
